Override `validator` on your `DateRangeSchema` class, e.g.:

```python
class DateRangeSchema(colander.MappingSchema):
    start = colander.SchemaNode(
        colander.DateTime(),
        missing=None, # Can’t be a callable?
        )
    end = colander.SchemaNode(
        colander.DateTime(),
        missing=None, # Can’t be a callable?
        )
    def validator(self, node, cstruct):
          start = cstruct['start']
          end = cstruct['end']
          if end is not None and start is not None and end <= start:
              raise colander.Invalid(node, 'end must fall after start')
```

